cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.DC, cs.DS, cs.CV

This paper discusses privacy-preserving deep learning and proposes a decentralized framework using blockchain technology. The paper also addresses fairness in collaborative deep learning. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CR (Cryptography and Security). The paper also involves machine learning and distributed systems, which are covered by cs.LG (Machine Learning) and cs.DC (Distributed, Parallel, and Cluster Computing). The paper uses benchmark image datasets, which falls under cs.CV (Computer Vision). Finally, the paper involves data privacy, which is covered by cs.DS (Data Structures and Algorithms).
